function.name: run_query
function.arguments:
{"query":"MATCH (d:biolink_Disease)-[r:biolink_has_phenotype]->(p:biolink_PhenotypicFeature {id: 'HP:0001263'})
WITH COLLECT(DISTINCT d.id) AS diseases_with_gdd
MATCH (d2:biolink_Disease)
WHERE NOT d2.id IN diseases_with_gdd
RETURN d2.name AS disease_name, d2.id AS disease_id LIMIT 10"}
